Package: eia
Title: US Energy Information Administration API
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew", "Leonawicz", email = "matt_leonawicz@esource.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9452-2771")),
    person(given = "E Source", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Provides API access to data from the US Energy Information Administration (EIA) <https://www.eia.gov/>. Use of the API requires a free API key obtainable at <https://www.eia.gov/opendata/register.php>.
    The package includes functions for accessing and searching EIA data categories, downloading time series datasets, and EIA geoset data. 
    Datasets returned by these functions are provided in a tidy format, or alternatively in a relatively unprocessed list based on the original JSON data.
